            "title": "A股跌轉升   深股升近1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股中段轉升，兩市成交合計11406.13億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指半日報3899點，升10點或0.26%，今日開跌0.95%或37點，報3652點，已為半日低位，即反覆向上，中段高見3902點，升13點或0.33%，半日成交4908.42億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指半日報13732，升125點或0.93%，今早開報13423，跌183點或1.34%，早段見13419，跌187點或1.37%，為上午低位，隨即向上，最高13733，升127點或0.93%，半日成交6497.71億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300半日報4495，升17點或0.4% ; 創業板指數升27點或0.83%，報3299。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15798860-a%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e8%bd%89%e5%8d%87-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%911",
